Not Everyone Wants To Be A winner, But Everyone Wants To Be Apart Of The Winning Team🏆-Tyree Wesley

Being a Serial Entrepreneur myself, I have learned that not everybody gets fullfillment out of being captain of their own winning team. Sometime just being tapped into the winning team brings them the feeling of success that they need to thrive. Playing your role on the team is just as essential to being a captain of your own.

💭Create a Vision 
🗺Give a Plan
🚀Execute with a Team

FOCUS ON YOUR VISION 🚀

👊Still A Winner In My Eyes 👊

Winners are not defined by the L’s that we take but by how many times we are willing to improve to fight another day.

Sometimes we need L’s so that we can dig deeper and bring out a different side of us that we didn’t know existed.
